♪I overrated myself♪

107
00:07:29,060 --> 00:07:33,330
♪When our stars cross paths again♪

108
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:36,080
♪Perhaps it's destiny♪

109
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:40,530
♪A thousand encounters♪

110
00:07:40,840 --> 00:07:43,220
♪All lead to you♪

111
00:07:43,610 --> 00:07:46,870
♪My unreasonable demands♪

112
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:51,280
♪Are precious emotions to you♪

113
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:56,550
♪I'm sure I am your♪

114
00:07:56,770 --> 00:07:58,870
♪Only one♪

115
